#

Lobster Roll

25 min
$30
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

shellfishglutendairy

Dietary Tags:

seafoodhigh protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

quickeasyluxury

Description

Indulge in a classic New England Lobster Roll, featuring succulent lobster meat in a buttery toasted bun.

Ingredients

  • lobster meat: 1 pound
  • hot dog buns: 4
  • mayonnaise: 1/4 cup
  • celery, diced: 1/2 cup
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • paprika: to taste
  • chives, chopped: 2 tablespoons
